{"tid":1379872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 我開始為到自己住康城而感到羞恥","createTime":"2019-07-29T01:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:00:43.000Z","uid":50442,"like":108,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a776836c09d31eb477832d80b16950b70d51bcbe","tid":1379872,"uid":50442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:09:39.000Z","msg":"本身已經對方國珊冇好感<br />\n直到上星期四有兩個自稱佢嘅支持者做撕紙狗<br />\n但前提係方國珊有喺69出嚟遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再者 由峻瀅行到地鐵站條隧道嘅連儂牆<br />\n基本上都係晏晝貼完 朝早就比人撕到全軍覆沒<br />\n可以堪稱全將軍澳撕得最快嘅連儂牆<br />\n到底成個康城住咗幾多藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呻完了 總之嚟緊嘅區議會選舉<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一票不投方國珊<br />\n食屎喇你</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4b1f69c244f551de2f864591a0ffe79c582aa7a","tid":1379872,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:12:59.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"3e28bca3283b9516822f3379d7045f91e6bdc52d","tid":1379872,"uid":50442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:54:20.000Z","msg":"推比康城人睇"},{"pid":"6b6d090d86c70c756d1f94beecf2383a75e89a78","tid":1379872,"uid":50442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4b1f69c244f551de2f864591a0ffe79c582aa7a","tid":1379872,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:12:59.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:54:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6249a8c9522a142eee951395732342a873e38d82","tid":1379872,"uid":29167,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy